parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The issue can cause confusion and uncertainty for the driver, potentially leading to accidents or safety risks while towing a trailer.
symptoms: Rapid flashing of the right turn signal when automatic headlights are activated or in the off position
dash error message
trailer lights malfunctioning or not working properly
especially at night.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the DEF heater can cause the vehicle to stall or become inoperable, leaving the driver stranded, especially in cold weather conditions.
symptoms: DEF tank freezing
vehicle unable to drive or idle
engine failure to run due to DEF system malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the trailer brake controller can cause a loss of trailer braking, leading to a serious safety concern while towing, potentially resulting in accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Intermittent "check trailer wiring" message on the dash
trailer brakes not functioning or functioning intermittently
brake controller malfunction
potential issue with solar chargers and batteries on RV affecting the trailer brake system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the trailer brake controller can cause the loss of trailer brakes, leading to a significant safety risk, especially when towing heavy loads.
symptoms: The "Check Trailer Wiring" warning appears on the dashboard
the trailer brakes are lost
the trailer indicator light goes off
the truck intermittently disconnects and reconnects from the trailer
the trailer brakes don't work briefly when the truck and trailer are disconnected.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Stalling and Loss of Power Assist
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden loss of engine power and power assist systems, such as brakes and power steering, can lead to a loss of control, increasing the risk of accidents, especially when towing heavy trailers.
symptoms: Engine stalling
loss of power steering
loss of brakes
warning lights on the dashboard
error messages on the digital display
such as "Service ECM" and "Service StabiliTrak".

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Abnormal noises and vibrations in the steering system can cause loss of control, especially when cornering, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: Knocking noise when turning corners
steering wheel turned to one side
vibrations in the steering wheel.
